'''嘉芙蓮·達迪·伍德'''（{{lang-en|Cathie Duddy Wood}}，1955年－），[[美國|美國]]金融分析師及企業家，現任[[方舟投資|方舟投資]]行政總裁及投資總裁，以投資[[破壞性創新|破壞性創新]]科技公司及其基金的高回報獲得廣泛關注，有「科技股女股神」的外號。<ref>{{cite web |title=科網女股神到底有多神！ 幾何級數增長 邏輯挑明星|url=https://udn.com/news/story/6849/3884466|work=聯合新聞網|language=zh|date=2019-06-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=逢低買進更有賺頭？科技女股神：暴跌的科技股帶來有趣的估值|url=https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4230316|work=鉅亨|language=zh|date=02-11-2018|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2018-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181102171645/https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4230316|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=美科網女股神 年賺43%的秘密|url=https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/investment/article/2148891/%E7%BE%8E%E7%A7%91%E7%B6%B2%E5%A5%B3%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%9E+%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%BA43%25%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86|work=信報|language=zh|date=2019-05-29|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030172535/http://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/investment/article/2148891/%E7%BE%8E%E7%A7%91%E7%B6%B2%E5%A5%B3%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%9E+%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%BA43%25%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Ark Invest內部政變 「連登契媽」Catherine Wood將被踢出ARK Invest ARKK、ARKF、Tesla將崩盤？|url=https://www.edigest.hk/%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87/ark-invest-%e5%85%a7%e9%83%a8%e6%94%bf%e8%ae%8a-%e9%80%a3%e7%99%bb%e5%a5%91%e5%aa%bd-catherine-wood-%e5%b0%87%e8%a2%ab%e8%b8%a2%e5%87%ba-ark-invest-arkk-arkf-tesla-%e5%b4%a9%e7%9b%a4-207820/|work=經濟一週|language=zh|date=2020-11-23}}</ref>

== 簡歷 ==
=== 早年經歷 ===
嘉芙蓮·伍德生於[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]，<ref name="BIO">{{cite web|title=Catherine Wood|url=https://citywireselector.com/manager/catherine-wood/d1079|work=Citywire Selector|language=en|date=2020|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115105622/http://citywireselector.com/manager/catherine-wood/d1079|dead-url=no}}</ref>
其父母為來自[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]的美國移民，在其成長之時曾積極鼓勵她找尋自己的夢想。<ref name="SE">{{cite web|title=Secret Sauce Behind Ark’s Success Is Cathie Wood’s Diverse Team|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-09-26/secret-sauce-behind-ark-success-is-cathie-wood-s-diverse-team|work=[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]|language=en|date=2020-09-26|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120201520/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-09-26/secret-sauce-behind-ark-success-is-cathie-wood-s-diverse-team|dead-url=no}}</ref>伍德的爸爸曾於[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]軍隊及[[美國空軍|美國空軍]]服務，其後成為一名成功的雷達系統工程師。由於其父非常注重細節，因此促使伍德發現事物之間的聯繫。<ref name="doneyet">{{Cite news | last=Liu | first=Evie | title=ARK’s Cathie Wood Disrupted Investment Management. She’s Not Done Yet. | url=https://www.barrons.com/articles/arks-cathie-wood-disrupted-investment-management-shes-not-done-yet-51614992508 | work=[[巴倫周刊|巴倫周刊]] | date=08-03-2021 | accessdate=2021-04-14 | archive-date=2021-06-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210628232758/https://www.barrons.com/articles/arks-cathie-wood-disrupted-investment-management-shes-not-done-yet-51614992508 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

其後，她在1974年於{{link-en|聖母學院 (洛杉磯)|Notre Dame Academy (Los Angeles, California)|聖母學院}}高中畢業後，<ref>{{cite web |title=NDA LAUNCHES DUDDY INNOVATION INSTITUTE|url=http://ndablog.weebly.com/blog/nda-launches-duddy-innovation-institute|work=Notre Dame Academy|language=en|date=03-08-2018}}</ref>於1981年在[[南加州大學|南加州大學]]獲得金融經濟學學士學位，並以最高級及優秀的[[拉丁文學位榮譽|拉丁文學位榮譽]]（''Summa Cum Laude''）畢業。<ref>{{cite web|title=Cathie Wood|url=https://www.afhu.org/2018/01/26/catherine-d-wood/|work=American Friends of the Hebrew University|language=en|date=|access-date=2020-09-27|archive-date=2021-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210613013158/https://www.afhu.org/2018/01/26/catherine-d-wood/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在南加州大學就讀期間，伍德以其傑出的表現給予著名經濟學家[[阿瑟·拉弗|阿瑟·拉弗]]（Arthur Laffer）很深的印象，而拉弗亦在之後指導伍德在經濟和商業領域上的發展，其後兩人亦持續聯絡，在很多層面上互相指教。<ref>{{cite web|title=How To Discover Surprisingly Innovative ETFs|url=https://www.markettamer.com/blog/active-innovation-through-innovation-based-etfs|work=Market Tamer|language=en|date=10-11-2014|access-date=2020-10-19|archive-date=2021-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210615161633/https://www.markettamer.com/blog/active-innovation-through-innovation-based-etfs|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 金融生涯 ===
1977年，她在導師拉弗的引薦下，在{{le|資本集團|Capital Group Companies}}公司獲助理經濟師職位，開始其金融分析師的職業生涯。<ref name="doneyet" /><ref name="BIO" />其後，她於1980年轉職Jennison Associates任首席經濟師。1981年，她曾提前成功預測[[通貨膨脹|通貨膨脹]]和[[利率|利率]]已經到達頂峰，但被當時的上司所白眼。同時，在1980年代初期，她曾與銀行家{{le|亨利·考夫曼|Henry Kaufman}}辯論為何她認為利率已經到頂。<ref name="doneyet" />此經驗令伍德認為違背所謂「共識」的潛力非常巨大，令她常以自身經驗反其道而行獲得成功。<ref name="CC">{{cite web|title=57歲才創業，花5年就登上最富有女性！她如何成為洞見特斯拉潛能的新時代股神？|url=https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/59997/cathie-wood|work=數位時代|language=zh|date=10-11-2020|accessdate=2020-11-20|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109060630/https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/59997/cathie-wood|dead-url=no}}</ref>1985年及1990年起，她兼任該公司的股票研究分析師及投資組合經理。<ref name="LINK">{{cite web |title=Cathie Wood|url=https://www.linkedin.com/in/catherinedwood/|work=Linkedin|language=en|date=}}</ref><ref name="BIO" />

1998年，伍德合夥成立對沖基金Tupelo Capital，任投資組合經理主理該基金的宏觀戰略。<ref name="LINK" />2000年，該基金一共管理8億美元的資產。<ref name="C2" />2001年，她轉到{{le|聯博資產管理|AllianceBernstein}}任投資長，負責管理基金達50億美元的投資組合。<ref name="C2">{{cite web|title=Catherine D. Wood|url=https://content.investmentsandwealth.org/catherine-d.-wood-un|work=Investments and Wealth Institute|language=en|date=|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805155041/https://content.investmentsandwealth.org/catherine-d.-wood-un|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[2007年–2008年環球金融危機|2007年–2008年環球金融危機]]中，伍德曾被批評其基金表現跑輸大市。<ref name="neverheard" /><ref>{{Cite news | last=Cuccinello | first=Hayley C. | website=[[福布斯|福布斯]] | date=2020-10-13 | title='Go For It': America's Richest Self-Made Women On Founding Businesses After 40 | url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/hayleycuccinello/2020/10/13/american-self-made-women-founders-over-40/ | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221145426/https://www.forbes.com/sites/hayleycuccinello/2020/10/13/american-self-made-women-founders-over-40/ | archive-date=2020-12-21 | accessdate=2021-04-14 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="neverheard">{{Cite news | title=Cathie Wood, the Best Investor You've Never Heard Of | url=https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-02-18/cathie-wood-s-tesla-bet-puts-ark-invest-in-spotlight | work=[[彭博新聞|彭博新聞]] | last=Winkler | first=Matthew A. | date=2020-02-18 | accessdate=2020-09-27 | archive-date=2020-08-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810065115/https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-02-18/cathie-wood-s-tesla-bet-puts-ark-invest-in-spotlight | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年，因聯博認為基於破壞性創新的[[交易型開放式指數基金|交易型開放式指數基金]]（ETF）的想法風險太大，伍德離開了聯博公司，並於同年1月成立[[方舟投資|方舟投資]]，<ref name=doneyet/><ref name=neverheard/><ref>{{Cite news | url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-14/cathie-wood-s-ark-gives-richard-branson-a-300-million-boost | last=Stupples | first=Ben | date=2021-01-14 | title=Cathie Wood's Ark Gives Richard Branson a $300 Million Boost | work=[[彭博新聞|彭博新聞]] | accessdate=2021-04-14 | archive-date=2021-04-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416030132/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-14/cathie-wood-s-ark-gives-richard-branson-a-300-million-boost | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | last1=Potter | first1=Sam | last2=Ballentine | first2=Claire | date=2021-01-14 | title=Cathie Wood's Vision for Space ETF Sends Industry Soaring | work=[[彭博新聞|彭博新聞]] | url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-14/cathie-wood-s-vision-for-space-etf-sends-whole-industry-soaring | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128100912/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-01-14/cathie-wood-s-vision-for-space-etf-sends-whole-industry-soaring | archive-date=2021-01-28 | accessdate=2021-04-14 | dead-url=no }}</ref>任該基金的行政總裁至今。<ref name="BIO" />方舟投資以[[約櫃|約櫃]]命名，而伍德在當時則讀了一年《[[聖經|聖經]]》。<ref name=meetark>{{Cite news | url=https://www.scmp.com/magazines/style/celebrity/article/3123779/cathie-wood-religious-reddit-hit-trump-supporter-meet-ark | title=Cathie Wood: religious, Reddit hit, Trump supporter? Meet Ark Invest’s rock star stock picker who even has her own merchandise | first=Dorothy | last=So | work=[[南華早報|南華早報]] | date=2021-03-03 | accessdate=2021-04-14 | archive-date=2021-05-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510144243/https://www.scmp.com/magazines/style/celebrity/article/3123779/cathie-wood-religious-reddit-hit-trump-supporter-meet-ark | dead-url=no }}</ref>

在創業初期，其公司在2014年至2016年間，基金排行處於同類基金的末端，亦需要靠伍德投入積蓄和出售股份維持運作。<ref name="CC" />但自2017年起，隨著公司持有的股票開始上漲，開始錄得持續增長。<ref name="CC" />

2020年，伍德被[[彭博社|彭博社]]榮譽退休[[總編輯|總編輯]]{{lk|溫以樂|Matthew Winkler (journalist)}}（Matthew A. Winkler）評選為2020年最佳選股人。<ref>{{Cite news | title=The Best Stock Picker of 2020 Wins With Disruptive DNA | first=Matthew A. | last=Winkler | work=[[彭博新聞|彭博新聞]] | url=https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-12-31/ark-s-cathie-wood-bets-on-dna-innovators | date=2020-12-31 | accessdate=2021-04-14 | archive-date=2021-02-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204222954/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=81135750-6738-11eb-977d-3559f3773b55&url=L29waW5pb24vYXJ0aWNsZXMvMjAyMC0xMi0zMS9hcmstcy1jYXRoaWUtd29vZC1iZXRzLW9uLWRuYS1pbm5vdmF0b3Jz | dead-url=no }}</ref>截至2021年3月，按淨資產總額計，伍德管理的兩隻基金在女性管理的10大基金中名列前茅。<ref>{{Cite news | last=Alladi | first=Amrutha | last2=Dibenedetto | first2=Gabrielle | title=The Percentage of U.S. Female Fund Managers Is Exactly Where It Was in 2000 | url=https://www.morningstar.com/articles/1029482/the-percentage-of-us-female-fund-managers-is-exactly-where-it-was-in-2000 | website=[[晨星公司|晨星公司]] | date=2021-03-16 | accessdate=2021-04-14 | archive-date=2021-06-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210630142421/https://www.morningstar.com/articles/1029482/the-percentage-of-us-female-fund-managers-is-exactly-where-it-was-in-2000 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 觀點 ==
=== 投資策略 ===
伍德認為傳統的大型基金對科技股的分析思維落後，難以與日新月異的科技時代並進，因此是她成立ARK Invest的主要原因。<ref name="IN">{{cite web|title=呢隻科網股ETF基金一年升逾80%！美國ARK前瞻性及表現分析｜精叻理財|url=https://www.businesstimes.com.hk/articles/128167/%E7%A7%91%E7%B6%B2%E8%82%A1-etf-%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8Bark-%E5%89%8D%E7%9E%BB%E6%80%A7-%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90-%E7%B2%BE%E5%8F%BB%E7%90%86%E8%B2%A1.htm|work=香港財經時報|language=zh|date=10-07-2020|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712205329/https://www.businesstimes.com.hk/articles/128167/%E7%A7%91%E7%B6%B2%E8%82%A1-etf-%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8Bark-%E5%89%8D%E7%9E%BB%E6%80%A7-%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90-%E7%B2%BE%E5%8F%BB%E7%90%86%E8%B2%A1.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>當中，其基金曾作出不少被市場認為是極度破格的投資策略，如在2015年時投資[[比特幣|比特幣]]，在兩年後該幣升至近二萬美元的歷史高位前，接近全數減持旗下基金持有的比特幣。<ref>{{cite web|title=Barely any bitcoin left in Ark ETFs|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2018/05/18/barely-any-bitcoin-left-in-ark-etfs.html|work=CNBC|language=en|date=2018-05-18|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109025744/https://www.cnbc.com/2018/05/18/barely-any-bitcoin-left-in-ark-etfs.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="IN" />

同時，伍德亦以其對[[特斯拉_(公司)|特斯拉]]的樂觀前景觀望聞名<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tesla Stock Is A Screaming Buy Now If Cathie Wood's ARK Is Right|url=https://www.investors.com/etfs-and-funds/sectors/tesla-stock-worth-exactly-much-now-cathie-woods-ark-says/|access-date=2021-06-22|date=2021-03-22|last=Daily|first=Investor's Business|work=Investor's Business Daily|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501214553/https://www.investors.com/etfs-and-funds/sectors/tesla-stock-worth-exactly-much-now-cathie-woods-ark-says/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在ARK Invest成立初期，她已將該公司的股票列為基金中第五大股份。在2016年至2018年市場質疑該公司的前景下，她繼續增持特斯拉的股票<ref>{{Cite web|title=ARK’s Price Target for Tesla in 2025 is $3,000 Per Share|url=https://ark-invest.com/articles/analyst-research/tesla-price-target-2/|access-date=2021-06-22|date=2021-03-19|work=ARK Invest|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624205420/https://ark-invest.com/articles/analyst-research/tesla-price-target-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Cathie Wood's Ark expects Tesla stock to reach $3000 by 2025|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-tesla-ark-invest-idUSKBN2BC0O9|newspaper=Reuters|date=2021-03-20|accessdate=2021-06-22|language=en|first=Reuters|last=Staff|archive-date=2021-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627232445/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-tesla-ark-invest-idUSKBN2BC0O9|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

至2018年8月，在該公司的股價徘徊在320元左右的水平時，伍德曾向[[伊隆·馬斯克|伊隆·馬斯克]]發公開信，指出特斯拉在五年內股價估值為每股700到4000美元之間，反對他提出私有化公司的提議。<ref>{{cite web|title=Dear Elon: An Open Letter Against Taking Tesla Private|url=https://ark-invest.com/market-commentary/tesla-private/|work=ARK Invest|language=en|date=2018-08-22|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214230718/https://ark-invest.com/market-commentary/tesla-private/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而馬斯克指出他和董事會在閱讀其信件後，影響了他們的決定。<ref name="PER" />2020年1月中，伍德將目標上調至6000美元，<ref>{{cite web|title=漲不停！大多頭高喊特斯拉股價未來5年破6000美元|url=https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3040778|work=自由時報|language=zh|date=2020-01-15|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200115173210/https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3040778|dead-url=no}}</ref>
至1月末ARK Invest更發表文章指出特斯拉股票的目標價為7000美元。<ref>{{cite web|title=Tesla’s Potential Trajectory During the Next Five Years|url=https://ark-invest.com/analyst-research/tesla-price-target/|work=ARK Invest|language=en|date=2020-01-31|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219115617/https://ark-invest.com/analyst-research/tesla-price-target/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=她喊特斯拉上看6800美元！美國新股神 投資只鎖定「這個」特質|url=https://www.wealth.com.tw/home/articles/27131|work=財訊|language=zh|date=2020-08-26|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127061318/https://www.wealth.com.tw/home/articles/27131|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 破壞性創新 ===
ARK Invest以投資[[人工智能|人工智能]]、[[能源|能源]]儲備（如[[電池|電池]]系統、[[電動汽車|電動汽車]]、[[自動駕駛|自動駕駛]]）、[[機器人|機器人]]技術、[[DNA測序|DNA測序]]及[[區塊鏈|區塊鏈]]技術五個創新領域為主。<ref>{{cite web|title=Invest In The Future Today|url=https://ark-invest.com/invest-in-innovation/|work=ARK Invest|language=en|date=2020|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113230637/https://ark-invest.com/invest-in-innovation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

伍德認為傳統的基金經理過於關注行業和短期價格走勢，無法關注破壞性創新公司所帶來的長期影響和增長潛力。<ref name="PHIL">{{cite web|title=THE ARK INVESTMENT PROCESS|url=https://research.ark-invest.com/hubfs/1_Download_Files_ARK-Invest/Marketing_Material/ARK-Invest-Thematic-Investment-Process.pdf|work=ARK Invest|language=en|date=2020|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922005202/https://research.ark-invest.com/hubfs/1_Download_Files_ARK-Invest/Marketing_Material/ARK-Invest-Thematic-Investment-Process.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>而她亦認為破壞性創新會導致成本快速下降，跨行業和地域化，並具有催生進一步創新的能力，從而在廣泛的時間範圍內實現增長。<ref name="PHIL" />

=== 公司組織 ===
與其餘投資基金不同，ARK Invest的分析師幾乎全數沒有財經背景，團隊曾從事不同科技行業，如為癌症研究人員、人工智能專家、遊戲工程師，甚至是帆船船長。<ref name="SE" />伍德認為分析師擁有從業科技業的經驗，已在新世界中站了腳，能夠理解科技如何運作，因而具有極強的創造力。<ref name="SE" />

同時，伍德亦積極創造多元就業環境，其基金內有四分之一的成員為[[有色人種|有色人種]]，當中的30%為女性，並以20多歲的人為多數。<ref name="SE" />

== 基金表現 ==
在2018年時，在美國上市的1818隻[[交易所買賣基金|交易所買賣基金]]（ETF）中，ARK Invest的三隻ETF是首十五名在三年內表現最好的基金。<ref>{{cite web|title=How Cathie Wood Bought Bitcoin and Ruled the ETF Rankings|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-09-24/how-cathie-wood-bought-bitcoin-and-ruled-the-etf-rankings/|work=[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]|language=en|date=2018-09-24|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127130656/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-09-24/how-cathie-wood-bought-bitcoin-and-ruled-the-etf-rankings|dead-url=no}}</ref>2020年，ARK Invest的創新ETF，在584隻擁有至少10億美元資產的全球基金中表現最佳，更在過去三年中以高達165%的回報率擊敗投行[[貝萊德|貝萊德]]的基金表現。<ref name="PER">{{cite web|title=Cathie Wood, the Best Investor You’ve Never Heard Of|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-02-18/cathie-wood-s-tesla-bet-puts-ark-invest-in-spotlight|work=[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]|language=en|date=2020-02-18|accessdate=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810065115/https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-02-18/cathie-wood-s-tesla-bet-puts-ark-invest-in-spotlight|dead-url=no}}</ref>

據[[彭博新聞社|彭博新聞社]]彙編的數據顯示，ARK Invest的基金自成立以來，收益幾乎是[[標準普爾500指數|標準普爾500指數]]的2.4倍，或[[納斯達克指數|納斯達克指數]]的1.7倍。<ref name="PER" />

== 個人生活相關 ==
=== 個人生活 ===
伍德本於[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]][[威爾頓_(康乃狄克州)|威爾頓]]居住，<ref name=forbesprofile>{{cite web |url=https://www.forbes.com/profile/cathie-wood/ |title=Forbes profile: Cathie Wood |publisher=[[福布斯|福布斯]] |access-date=2021-04-14 |archive-date=2021-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416113806/https://www.forbes.com/profile/cathie-wood/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>但在[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]爆發後，她於[[南卡羅來納州|南卡羅來納州]][[希爾頓黑德島_(南卡羅來納州)|希爾頓黑德島]]中購買了房子，並遷至那裡遙距工作。<ref>{{Cite web|title=How Cathie Wood Beat Wall Street By Betting Tesla Is Worth More Than $1 Trillion|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/antoinegara/2020/10/05/how-cathie-wood-beat-wall-street-by-betting-tesla-is-worth-more-than-1-trillion/?sh=6f6ed9513d45|work=[[福布斯|福布斯]]|language=en|date=2020-10-05|access-date=2021-04-14|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414162329/https://www.forbes.com/sites/antoinegara/2020/10/05/how-cathie-wood-beat-wall-street-by-betting-tesla-is-worth-more-than-1-trillion/?sh=6f6ed9513d45|dead-url=no}}</ref>她已與前夫羅伯特·伍德（Robert Wood）離婚，他亦於2018年去世。她有三個孩子：凱特琳（Caitlin）、卡羅琳（Caroline）和羅伯特（Robert）。<ref name=godswork>{{Cite news | title=Cathie Wood: a tech investor doing God’s work | work=[[金融時報_(英國)|金融時報]] | url=https://www.ft.com/content/4df2b4cf-2ffe-4db5-9594-47e05e1e2240 | date=12-03-2021 | accessdate=2021-04-14 | archive-date=2021-05-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513053747/https://www.ft.com/content/4df2b4cf-2ffe-4db5-9594-47e05e1e2240 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.legacy.com/obituaries/stamfordadvocate/obituary.aspx?n=robert-wood&pid=190805378&fhid=29310 |title=Robert Wood |publisher={{le|Legacy.com|Legacy.com}} |access-date=2021-04-14 |archive-date=2021-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416231821/https://www.legacy.com/obituaries/stamfordadvocate/obituary.aspx?n=robert-wood&pid=190805378&fhid=29310 |dead-url=no }}</ref>伍德有散步的興趣，通常在每天早晨的五個小時的虛擬會議後就會前往散步。<ref name="citywire" /><ref name="day" /> 她通常在早上七時起床，並開始閱讀研究報告。<ref name="day">{{cite news | url=https://finance.yahoo.com/news/ark-invest-cathie-wood-typical-day-142448727.html | title=A typical day for Ark Invest's star stock picker Cathie Wood | first=Jen | last=Rogers | work={{le|雅虎財經頻道|Yahoo! Finance}} | date=06-02-2021 | accessdate=2021-04-14 | archive-date=2021-03-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317061019/https://finance.yahoo.com/news/ark-invest-cathie-wood-typical-day-142448727.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

伍德是虔誠的基督徒。<ref name=meetark/> 她每天早上一邊泡咖啡一邊閱讀《[[聖經|聖經]]》，<ref name=godswork/>並且是當地教會的活躍成員。<ref name=citywire>{{cite web |url=https://citywire.co.uk/funds-insider/manager/catherine-wood/d1079 |title=Catherine Wood |publisher={{le|Citywire|Citywire}} |access-date=2021-04-14 |archive-date=2021-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210415034001/https://citywire.co.uk/funds-insider/manager/catherine-wood/d1079 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2018年，她向出身的高中捐贈資金成立Duddy創新學院，該學院鼓勵女孩學習破壞性創新。<ref>{{Cite web | title=Duddy Innovation Institute – Duddy Innovation Institute – Notre Dame Academy | url=https://academy.ndasla.org/apps/pages/index.jsp?uREC_ID=1452845&type=d&pREC_ID=1612162 | publisher={{link-en|聖母學院 (洛杉磯)|Notre Dame Academy (Los Angeles, California)|聖母學院}} | access-date=2021-04-14 | archive-date=2021-04-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416113429/https://academy.ndasla.org/apps/pages/index.jsp?uREC_ID=1452845&type=d&pREC_ID=1612162 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

